text: Would you rather be covered head to toe in Peanut Butter, or Jelly?
If you were going to be any sort of insect, what insect would you be?
Do you think you could survive on a deserted island for a year?
Do you wash your hands everytime you use the bathroom?
Are you afraid of the dark?
Do you think sunsets or sunrises are more beautiful?
What did you want to be when you grow up?
